{"title":"问问他","authors":["张志民"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":7,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"问问他"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张志民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最近我从农村来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带来几句庄稼话："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说我们过得没以前好？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有眼的就该瞧见吧："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再没叫花子满街串，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再不掀锅没米下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三十儿晚上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再没账主子逼死人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十冬腊月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再不只披件破单褂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扛长工的儿子上了大学，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喂猪的穿上了“毡疙疸”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问问他——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这不叫提高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难道叫“低啦”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说合作社不行？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没瞧见也该听见吧："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"猪多啦，羊多啦，粮食多啦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穷少啦，病少啦，懒汉少啦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孤老有人管，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灾荒有办法，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个人单干"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁种地使得起拖拉机？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖祖辈辈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁给俺们村作过“规划”？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年一亩打石五，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明年一亩要打石八……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问问他——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这不叫优越，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难道叫“垮啦”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么说——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有“黄世仁”家。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}